data.description: Seize the opportunity! This residence is an ideal choice for a new family or couple seeking a home with sturdy foundations and the potential to personalize it to their liking. Nestled in a delightful neighborhood, it offers convenient proximity to downtown Newnan, Ashley Park, and I-85.    This home boasts well-maintained HVAC, Furnace, and Water Heater, ensuring reliability. Notably, the roof underwent replacement in 2019, and the patio deck received a fresh refinishing in 2023. Revel in the charm of hardwood flooring throughout most of the house, complemented by tiled bathrooms.    Perfect for entertaining, the expansive patio deck in the back enhances the home's allure. A generously-sized recreation room, doubling as a potential bedroom, awaits, spacious enough for a pool table or a home theater system for guests. This room features a new AC/Heater system for added comfort.    The Master bedroom impresses with its roomy layout, a large walk-in closet, and an open area that can serve as a home office or study space. Bedrooms offer ample space, one even featuring a higher ceiling. Lastly, the interconnected living room and dining room create a harmonious open floor plan.    Welcome home to a residence that combines comfort, practicality, and the potential for unforgettable gatherings!
